reviewText: Great movies. As almost always is the case, the first is the best, with the sequels being not quite as good, but still enjoyable.
Good action packed movie . Good acting with alot of drama.

I enjoyed all of the "Hunger Games" movies for their entertainment value and the wonderful skills of the talented actors. The determining factor that inspired me to issue a 4-star rating rather than 5 stars is my personal belief that, had I not read the trilogy prior to viewing the movie versions, I would have been a bit confused at times due to the lack of detail and background information to explain the logic and reasoning behind a few of the characters' specific attitudes and responses to certain situations. That said; I would recommend the movies to audiences from age 16 and up.
